short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Provides an interface to Artemis for various Chrome APIs

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Artemis RGB Chrome extension allows you to enable layers, profiles, and more based on things happening in your browser.

You need the Artemis software in order to use this extension. https://artemis-rgb.com
